2013年，[[联邦总务署|美国总务管理局]]将该房产租赁[[川普集团|川普集团]]租赁此物业140年<ref>{{cite web |last=Grant |first=Peter |url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/trump-hotel-in-washington-d-c-to-open-ahead-of-schedule-1454901018 |title=Trump Hotel in Washington, D.C., to Open Ahead of Schedule |publisher=The Wall Street Journal |date=2016-02-08 |accessdate=2016-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160208042847/http://www.wsj.com/articles/trump-hotel-in-washington-d-c-to-open-ahead-of-schedule-1454901018 |archive-date=2016-02-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，建成豪华酒店。美食广场和商店在2014年1月关闭，<ref>{{cite web |last=Yates |first=Clinton |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/local/wp/2014/04/30/old-post-office-building-sees-dreary-final-days/ |title=Old Post Office building sees dreary final days |publisher=The Washington Post |date=2014-06-26 |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612012031/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/local/wp/2014/04/30/old-post-office-building-sees-dreary-final-days/ |archive-date=2014-06-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其余办公室和钟楼在2014年5月1日关闭，开始改造<ref name="SernovitzHurry">{{cite news|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/washington/breaking_ground/2014/04/hotel-conversion-to-close-off-old-post-office.html|last=Sernovitz|first=Daniel J.|title=Want to Visit the Old Post Office Tower? Better Hurry|newspaper=Washington Business Journal|date=April 24, 2014|accessdate=April 25, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140516072427/http://www.bizjournals.com/washington/breaking_ground/2014/04/hotel-conversion-to-close-off-old-post-office.html|archive-date=2014-05-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。'''华盛顿特区特朗普国际酒店'''于 2016年9月开业。

大楼高315英尺（96米），设有"国会钟"，其观景平台可欣赏到城市及其周边地区的全景。

